pid":"7d55265d80a43ab36ba1625ac1be7a7cb917ff67","tid":2092310,"uid":205733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:43:52.000Z","msg":"CRE aptitude test:<br />\n「政府很快會刊登憲報，要公務員宣誓及強制放棄BNO」並無此事<br />\n假如以上屬實：<br />\n可能性1：政府以不快的速度刊登憲報，要公務員宣誓及強制放棄BNO<br />\n可能性2：政府不會以刊登憲報的方式，要公務員宣誓及強制放棄BNO<br />\n可能性3：政府很快會刊登憲報，要公務員宣誓及自願放棄BNO<br />\n可能性4：政府很快會刊登憲報，要公務員宣誓及強制放棄BNO及其他國家護照<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7255280a37d7a522f1e6727e47ef9e4eefcc1030","tid":2092310,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"有 BNO 公務員最好快啲走啦，唔係保皇黨議員同政府遲早落閘，迫公務員交心，咁到時就走條撚。"},{"pid":"2e4b1f98ed9ac70b694cfa9a46714bf85bc510f5","tid":2092310,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:57:26.000Z","msg":"推 國際戰線 全民配合制裁<br />\n舉報輸入軍民兩用科技設備公司<br />\n舉報熱線: <a href=\"https://www.oig.doc.gov/Pages/Hotline.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oig.doc.gov%2FPages%2FHotline.aspx&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXKC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=1e0b5188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.oig.doc.gov/Pages/Hotline.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"5f23ea1f4e4bed8b5726eedf1c34431ccd00dbb7","tid":2092310,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"全香港唯一有士氣系統既兵種, 好驚佢地又士氣低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e9a985e042b7b8ba34eba5bad0b75569074919","tid":2092310,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit